%% SC-14 · 家长监督视图（家庭组）· owner=[s8, s5, s3] · mockup=P19 observer
flowchart TD
  Start([家长打开 P19 Observer]) --> CheckFamily[GET /family/members]
  CheckFamily --> HasChild{绑定孩子?}
  HasChild -->|否| InviteCTA[显示邀请 CTA · POST /family/invite]
  HasChild -->|是| ChildList[显示孩子列表]
  ChildList --> SelectChild[选某孩子]
  SelectChild --> PrivacyCheck{孩子隐私模式?}
  PrivacyCheck -->|开| AggregateOnly[仅显示聚合 · SC-09 top3]
  PrivacyCheck -->|关| FullView[显示完整学情 + 最近错题]
  AggregateOnly --> FetchStats[GET /review-stats?user_id=child&range=week · S5 提供数据源]
  FullView --> FetchStats
  FetchStats --> RenderChart[渲染趋势 + Top3 薄弱卡]
  RenderChart --> Interact{家长操作}
  Interact -->|切换孩子| SelectChild
  Interact -->|查错题| FetchWrong[GET /wrongbook/items?user_id=child&aggregate=true]
  Interact -->|邀请另一孩子| InviteCTA
